manifest.name: Obligator
manifest.description: A fully featured replacement for the built-in daily notes plugin. Obligator functions like a virtual bullet journal by copying over unchecked to-do items to your new daily note, along with adding any scheduled items you've set up
manifest.author: Dimitar Dimitrov
